Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community,
Having regard to Council Decision No 38/390/EEC of 11 July 1988 on special support for the development of agricultural statistics in Ireland (1), and in particular Article 4 thereof,
Whereas, as required by Article 4 (1) of the said Decision the Irish Government has submitted the annual programme of measures planned for 1989;
Whereas the programme that has been submitted is such as to attain the objectives of organizing in Ireland a system of surveys on agricultural matters which will satisfy Community requirements in respect of statistical information in this field;
